structure.unit: COUNTIES, CITIES, AND OTHER LOCAL UNITS
REVENUE BONDS FOR MISCELLANEOUS CITY OR COUNTY PROJECTS

law.text: Nothing in KRS 103.200 or 103.210 confers nor shall be deemed to confer the power of eminent domain except as provided by KRS 103.245.
law.history: Created 1980 Ky. Acts ch. 339, sec. 4, effective July 15, 1980.
